name: Selasar Imajinasi "Forest Bathing"
description: After the long journey, the feeling of tiredness must have enveloped us. Take a break! Walking into the middle of the forest for relaxation is not a problem. Enjoy the breeze and immerse ourselves in the dream world. The next journey will require energy, readiness, and staying alert. Apart from having lots of fun and amazing things, no one knows the obstacles that come our way.
